org.hibernate.query.sqm.function

Interface SqmFunction<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.hibernate.query.sqm.sql.internal.DomainResultProducer<T>, Expression<T>, JpaCriteriaNode, JpaExpression<T>, JpaFunction<T>, JpaSelection<T>, JpaTupleElement<T>, Selection<T>, Serializable, SqmExpression<T>, SqmNode, SqmSelectableNode<T>, SqmTypedNode<T>, SqmVisitableNode, TupleElement<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    org.hibernate.query.sqm.produce.function.internal.SelfRenderingSqmFunction, SqmJdbcFunctionEscapeWrapper

    public interface SqmFunction<T>
extends SqmExpression<T>, JpaFunction<T>, org.hibernate.query.sqm.sql.internal.DomainResultProducer<T>
    Contract for functions impls that would like to control the translation of the SQM expression into the SQL AST function

    #convertToSqlAst is the main contract here. It will be called as we walk the SQM tree to generate SQL AST and asked to produce the equivalent SQL AST expression
